Package: artR
Title: Aligned Rank TransformR
Description: artR is an R port of Jacob Wobbrock's C# ARTool.
    In a nutshell, the Aligned Rank Transform (ART) allows using
    parametric tests on nonparametric data. artR (and ARTool)
    applies this transformation on an input dataset, and generates
    a new dataset with extra aligned and ranked columns. artR allows
    applying this transform within R, avoiding the need for an
    external, Windows-only step in the data-analysis workflow.
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: person("Juan Sebastian", "Casallas", role = c("cre", "trl"),
